    <item>
      <title>戴森暂停马来西亚吹风机业务并重新部署员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/dyson-dials-back-malaysia-hairdryer-operations-redeploys-staff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，戴森有限公司 (Dyson Ltd.) 正在减少其在马来西亚的吹风机相关业务，因为这家消费品公司正在寻求精简其在该地区的业务，这些知情人士拒绝透露姓名，因为谈论的是私人问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/dyson-dials-back-malaysia-hairdryer-operations-redeploys-staff</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 02:38:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>首席财务官称沙特阿美将承担更多债务，重点关注股息增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/aramco-to-take-on-more-debt-focus-on-dividend-growth-cfo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯石油公司财务总监表示，该公司计划承担更多债务，并将重点关注股息的“价值和增长”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/aramco-to-take-on-more-debt-focus-on-dividend-growth-cfo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 02:17:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼放弃 6 亿美元债券，美国指控后债券价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/adani-bonds-tumble-after-founder-charged-by-us-authorities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国检察官指控创始人 Gautam Adani 参与贿赂阴谋后，Adani Group 旗下子公司取消了 6 亿美元的债券发行。该集团现有的美元纸币在亚洲交易中暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/adani-bonds-tumble-after-founder-charged-by-us-authorities</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 00:53:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币创下 95,000 美元新高，加密货币寻求与特朗普直接沟通</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/bitcoin-btc-on-verge-of-95-000-as-crypto-seeks-direct-line-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着数字资产行业推动在白宫设立一个专门负责加密货币政策的新职位，以巩固其对唐纳德·特朗普的影响力，比特币首次突破 95,000 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/bitcoin-btc-on-verge-of-95-000-as-crypto-seeks-direct-line-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 00:50:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Byju 创始人被指控试图利用隐藏现金重获公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/byju-accused-of-trying-to-use-missing-loan-cash-to-buy-back-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一份新的法庭文件显示，破产的印度科技公司 Byju’s 的创始人试图利用他向美国贷方隐瞒的贷款收益秘密回购一家被美国受托人接管的软件公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/byju-accused-of-trying-to-use-missing-loan-cash-to-buy-back-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 00:43:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑石集团向 Lancium AI 建设投资 5 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/blackstone-invests-500-million-in-lancium-ai-buildout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，黑石公司向 Lancium 公司投资逾 5 亿美元，后者正在西德克萨斯州建设超过 5 千兆瓦的数据中心，以满足人工智能应用日益增长的能源需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/blackstone-invests-500-million-in-lancium-ai-buildout</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 00:35:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
